---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Data Access — API & Downloads | HormuzWatch" description="Access HormuzWatch data via API. Dashboard data, oil prices, AIS ship tracking, and crisis timeline available programmatically.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <nav class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> <span class="mx-2">›</span> <span class="text-white">Data</span>
    </nav>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Data Access</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">API Endpoints</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">HormuzWatch provides free API access to all monitoring data. All endpoints return JSON and are updated in real-time.</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">GET</span>
              <code class="text-sm text-white font-mono">/api/dashboard</code>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-3">Complete dashboard data including strait status, ship counts, oil prices, insurance, diplomacy, timeline, and news.</p>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded p-3 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto">
              <div>curl https://hormuzwatch.com/api/dashboard</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">GET</span>
              <code class="text-sm text-white font-mono">/api/oil</code>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-3">Oil and energy price data including Brent, WTI, TTF gas, and gasoline prices.</p>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded p-3 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto">
              <div>curl https://hormuzwatch.com/api/oil</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">GET</span>
              <code class="text-sm text-white font-mono">/api/ais</code>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-3">AIS ship tracking data for the Strait of Hormuz region including vessel counts by type.</p>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded p-3 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto">
              <div>curl https://hormuzwatch.com/api/ais</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Response Format</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4">All API responses follow this structure:</p>
        <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded p-4 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto">
          <pre>{`{
  "success": true,
  "data": { ... },
  "timestamp": "2026-05-26T03:00:07.573Z"
}`}</pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Rate Limits</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">API endpoints are cached for 30-60 seconds. Please avoid polling more frequently than once per minute. All data is licensed under CC BY 4.0 — you are free to share and adapt with attribution.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
